  ⚠ eslint-plugin-unicorn(prefer-add-event-listener): Prefer `addEventListener()` over their `on`-function counterparts.
   ╭─[prefer_add_event_listener.tsx:1:5]
 1 │ foo.onclick = () => {}
   ·     ───────
   ╰────
  help: Replace `foo.onclick = () => {}` with `foo.addEventListener('click', () => {})`.

